      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust BMW M3 (E46) powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This specimen features a recently overhauled dual-VANOS system and a reinforced rear subframe, addressing critical chassis rigidity concerns. The naturally aspirated powerplant breathes through individual throttle bodies, delivering linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and an M-Variable limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry remains tight with upgraded polyurethane bushings, ensuring precise turn-in and cornering kinematics. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the drivetrain is in top form with documented valve adjustments and consistent compression across all six cylinders.",
